<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MangoThePug Viewer</title>
    <style>
      body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }

      #viewer {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        image-rendering: pixelated;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      #numberInput {
        position: absolute;
        display: none;
        padding: 10px;
        width: 120px;
        text-align: center;
        z-index: 10;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      #inscInput {
        position: absolute;
        display: none;
        padding: 10px;
        width: 120px;
        text-align: center;
        z-index: 10;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      #viewer img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: contain;
        image-rendering: pixelated;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="viewer">
      <input
        id="numberInput"
        type="number"
        placeholder="Enter Block Number"
        min="0"
        step="1"
      />
      <input
        id="inscInput"
        type="string"
        placeholder="Enter Inscription ID"
        min="0"
        step="1"
      />
    </div>

      if (mintText.includes("MINT_INSCRIPTION_ID")) {
        let blkInput = document.getElementById("numberInput");
        blkInput.style.display = "block";
        blkInput.style.position = "absolute";
        blkInput.style.fontSize = "10px";
        blkInput.style.margin = "5px";
        blkInput.style.left = "5px";
        blkInput.style.top = "5px";
        blkInput.value = blockNumber;

        blkInput.addEventListener("input", (event) => {
          blockNumber = blkInput.value;
          generateImage();
        });

        let insInput = document.getElementById("inscInput");
        insInput.style.display = "block";
        insInput.style.position = "absolute";
        insInput.style.fontSize = "10px";
        insInput.style.margin = "5px";
        insInput.style.left = "5px";
        insInput.style.top = "40px";
        insInput.placeholder = inscriptionID;

        insInput.addEventListener("input", async (event) => {
          inscriptionID = insInput.value;
          let inscriptionInfo = await fetch(
            "/r/inscription/" + inscriptionID
          ).then((r) => r.json());
          pugBlockNumber = inscriptionInfo.height;
          let blockinfo = await fetch("/r/blockinfo/" + pugBlockNumber).then(
            (r) => r.json()
          );
          nonce = blockinfo.nonce;
          console.log(nonce);
          generateImage();
        });

        generateImage();
      } else {
        const request = new XMLHttpRequest();
        try {
          request.open("GET", "/content/" + mintText);
          request.responseType = "text";
          request.addEventListener("load", () => initialize(request.response));
          request.addEventListener("error", () => console.error("XHR error"));
          request.send();
        } catch (error) {
          console.error(`XHR error ${request.status}`);
        }
      }
      async function initialize(result) {
        if (result) {
          let data = JSON.parse(result);
          blockNumber = data.blk;
          let inscriptionInfo = await fetch("/r/inscription/" + mintText).then(
            (r) => r.json()
          );
          pugBlockNumber = inscriptionInfo.height;
          let blockinfo = await fetch("/r/blockinfo/" + pugBlockNumber).then(
            (r) => r.json()
          );
          nonce = blockinfo.nonce;
          inscriptionID = mintText;
        }
        generateImage();
      }

      function createImageElement(base64String) {
        const img = document.createElement("img");
        img.src = `data:image/png;base64,${base64String}`;
        img.style.position = "absolute";
        img.style.width = "100%";
        img.style.objectFit = "contain";
        img.style.imageRendering = "pixelated";
        return img;
      }

      function generateImage() {
        const root = document.getElementById("viewer");

        root.querySelectorAll("img").forEach((img) => img.remove());

        const blockStr = blockNumber.toString();
        const nonceStr = nonce.toString();
        const idNumbersOnly = inscriptionID.replace(/[^0-9]/g, "");
        const randNum = BigInt(idNumbersOnly) * BigInt(nonce);
        const randNumStr = randNum.toString();

        const randomNumberStr = randNumStr.substring(0, 6);

        const firstDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 1
            ? blockStr[blockStr.length - blockStr.length]
            : undefined;
        const fifthLastDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 5 ? blockStr[blockStr.length - 5] : undefined;
        const fourthLastDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 4 ? blockStr[blockStr.length - 4] : undefined;
        const thirdLastDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 3 ? blockStr[blockStr.length - 3] : undefined;
        const secondLastDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 2 ? blockStr[blockStr.length - 2] : undefined;
        const lastDigit =
          blockStr.length >= 1 ? blockStr[blockStr.length - 1] : undefined;

        // 1. Add background
        if (blockStr.length < 6) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.background[0].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg);
        } else if (fifthLastDigit == 0) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[0].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg); //Rainbow
        } else if (fifthLastDigit == 5) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[1].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg); //Natrix
        } else if (fifthLastDigit == 9) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[3].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg); //Mondrian
        } else if (fifthLastDigit == 3) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[4].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg); //DMT
        } else if (firstDigit !== undefined && blockStr.length > 5) {
          const BGImg = createImageElement(traits.background[firstDigit].data);
          root.appendChild(BGImg);
        }

        // 2. Add base traits (Face, Ears, Body, Eyes, Nose/Mouth)
        if (secondLastDigit !== undefined) {
          const faceImg = createImageElement(traits.face[secondLastDigit].data);
          root.appendChild(faceImg);
        }
        if (thirdLastDigit !== undefined) {
          const earsImg = createImageElement(traits.ears[thirdLastDigit].data);
          root.appendChild(earsImg);
        }
        if (
          secondLastDigit !== undefined &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8888")
        ) {
          const bodyImg = createImageElement(traits.body[secondLastDigit].data);
          root.appendChild(bodyImg);
        }
        if (lastDigit !== undefined) {
          const eyesImg = createImageElement(traits.eyes[lastDigit].data);
          root.appendChild(eyesImg);
        }
        if (lastDigit !== undefined) {
          const nosemouthImg = createImageElement(
            traits.noseMouth[lastDigit].data
          );
          root.appendChild(nosemouthImg);
        }

        // 3. Add emotions
        if (fifthLastDigit !== undefined) {
          const emoImg = createImageElement(
            traits.emotion[fifthLastDigit].data
          );
          root.appendChild(emoImg);
        }

        // 4. Add accessories and/or collar
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("78")) {
          const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[1].data);
          root.appendChild(accsImg); //Left Earring
        }
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("80")) {
          const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[0].data);
          root.appendChild(accsImg); //Right Earring
        }
        if (randomNumberStr > 1 && randomNumberStr % 423 == 0) {
          const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[4].data);
          root.appendChild(accsImg); //Hoop Earrings
        }
        if (
          fourthLastDigit !== undefined &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("79") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("282") &&
          !(randomNumberStr > 1 && randomNumberStr % 514 == 0) &&
          !(
            (randomNumberStr.includes("17") && randomNumberStr % 74 == 0) ||
            (randomNumberStr % 17 == 0 && randomNumberStr.includes("74"))
          )
        ) {
          const collarImg = createImageElement(
            traits.collar[fourthLastDigit].data
          );
          root.appendChild(collarImg);
        }

        // 5. Add jail fit
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("666")) {
          const clothingImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[3].data);
          root.appendChild(clothingImg); //Prison Costume
        }

        // 6. If no costume, 7. if bat/cat mask
        if (
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8888") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("0000") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8484")
        ) {
          if (
            randomNumberStr.includes("217") ||
            randomNumberStr.includes("317")
          ) {
            // inscrmouthtraits, else if mouthtraits
            if (randomNumberStr.includes("7979")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[7].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Gold Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("420")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[6].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //CBD Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("111")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[5].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("912")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[1].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Green Candle
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("125")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[2].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Red Candle
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 2) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[0].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Left Tooth
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && Number(fourthLastDigit) >= 4) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[1].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue Up
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && fourthLastDigit < 4) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 4) {
              if (fourthLastDigit < 8) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[2].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue Down
              } else if (fourthLastDigit > 7) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
              }
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 6) {
              if (fourthLastDigit >= 1) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[3].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Right Tooth
              } else if (fourthLastDigit < 1) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
              }
            }
            // Mask
            if (randomNumberStr.includes("217")) {
              const maskImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[12].data);
              root.appendChild(maskImg); //Bat Mask
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("317")) {
              const maskImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[14].data);
              root.appendChild(maskImg); //Cat Mask
            }
          }
        }

        // 8. If gas/face
        if (
          randomNumberStr.includes("2019") ||
          randomNumberStr.includes("333")
        ) {
          if (thirdLastDigit == 2) {
            const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[0].data);
            root.appendChild(mtImg); //Left Tooth
          } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && Number(fourthLastDigit) >= 4) {
            const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[1].data);
            root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue up
          } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && fourthLastDigit < 4) {
            const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
            root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
          } else if (thirdLastDigit == 4) {
            if (fourthLastDigit < 8) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[2].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue Down
            } else if (fourthLastDigit > 7) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
            }
          } else if (thirdLastDigit == 6) {
            if (fourthLastDigit >= 1) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[3].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Right Tooth
            } else if (fourthLastDigit < 1) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
            }
          }
          if (randomNumberStr.includes("2019")) {
            const maskImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[11].data);
            root.appendChild(maskImg); //Face Mask
          } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("333")) {
            const maskImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[10].data);
            root.appendChild(maskImg); //Gas Mask
          }
        }

        // 9. Add eyewear if not bat/cat
        if (
          !randomNumberStr.includes("217") & !randomNumberStr.includes("317")
        ) {
          // insceyewear, else if royals eyewear, else if eyewear
          if (
            randomNumberStr.includes("13") ||
            randomNumberStr.includes("89")
          ) {
            const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[0].data);
            root.appendChild(ewImg); //Red Eyes
          }
          if (!randomNumberStr.includes("8888")) {
            if (randomNumberStr.includes("144")) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[1].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Monocle
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("233")) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[3].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Future Glasses
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("719")) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[4].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Tap Glasses
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("2009")) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[5].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //BTC Glasses
            } else if (
              blockStr % 35 == 0 &&
              !(blockStr % 220 == 0) &&
              !(blockStr % 33 == 0) &&
              !(blockStr % 12 == 0 && !blockStr % 56 == 0)
            ) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsEyewear[2].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Red Noun
            } else if (
              blockStr % 37 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 35 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 220 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 33 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 12 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 56 == 0
            ) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsEyewear[3].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Red Noun
            } else if (
              blockStr % 44 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 37 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 35 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 220 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 33 == 0 &&
              !(blockStr % 12 == 0 && !blockStr % 56 == 0) &&
              !blockStr % 39 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 31 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 32 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 34 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 40 == 0 &&
              !blockStr % 38 == 0
            ) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsEyewear[1].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //VR Headset
            } else if (
              parseInt(String(blockStr).slice(-4)) < 3700 &&
              String(blockStr).includes("07")
            ) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsEyewear[0].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Laser Eyes
            } else if (secondLastDigit == 0) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[0].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Reading Glasses
            } else if (secondLastDigit == 3 && thirdLastDigit !== undefined) {
              if (thirdLastDigit <= 3) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[1].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //Heart Glasses
              } else if (thirdLastDigit >= 4) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[4].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //Blue Shades
              }
            } else if (secondLastDigit == 7 && thirdLastDigit !== undefined) {
              if (["0", "2", "4", "6", "8"].includes(thirdLastDigit)) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[2].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //3D Glasses
              } else if (["1", "3", "5", "7", "9"].includes(thirdLastDigit)) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[5].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //Trippy Glasses
              }
            } else if (secondLastDigit == 9 && thirdLastDigit !== undefined) {
              if (
                ["0", "4", "5", "6", "7", "8", "9"].includes(thirdLastDigit)
              ) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[3].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //Black Shades
              } else if (["1", "2", "3"].includes(thirdLastDigit)) {
                const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.eyewearTraits[6].data);
                root.appendChild(ewImg); //Jet Black Shades
              }
            } else if (
              randomNumberStr > 1 &&
              (randomNumberStr % 44 == 0 || randomNumberStr % 56 == 0)
            ) {
              const ewImg = createImageElement(traits.extraEyewear[2].data);
              root.appendChild(ewImg); //Blindfold
            }
          }
          if (
            !randomNumberStr.includes("2019") &&
            !randomNumberStr.includes("333")
          ) {
            // 10. Add inscrmouthtraits, else if mouthtraits
            if (randomNumberStr.includes("7979")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[7].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Gold Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("420")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[6].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //CBD Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("111")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[5].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Bone
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("912")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[1].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Green Candle
            } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("125")) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[2].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Red Candle
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 2) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[0].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Left Tooth
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && Number(fourthLastDigit) >= 4) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[1].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue Up
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 3 && fourthLastDigit < 4) {
              const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
              root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 4) {
              if (fourthLastDigit < 8) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[2].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Tongue Down
              } else if (fourthLastDigit > 7) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
              }
            } else if (thirdLastDigit == 6) {
              if (fourthLastDigit >= 1) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[3].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Right Tooth
              } else if (fourthLastDigit < 1) {
                const mtImg = createImageElement(traits.mouthTraits[4].data);
                root.appendChild(mtImg); //Both Teeth
              }
            }
          }
        }

        // 11. Add Headgear if no clothing or costume
        if (
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8888") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("0000") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8484") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("217") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("317") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("400") &&
          !(
            randomNumberStr.includes("8") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("0") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("1") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("5") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("2")
          )
        ) {
          // inscheadgear, else if royals headgear, else if headgear
          if (
            randomNumberStr.includes("1984") ||
            (randomNumberStr % 1984 == 0 && randomNumberStr > 1)
          ) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[15].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Royal Tiara
          } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("273")) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[9].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //BTC Hat
          } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("712")) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[0].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Graduation Cap
          } else if (
            lastDigit == 3 &&
            blockStr.includes("43") &&
            !blockStr.includes("8") &&
            !blockStr.includes("6") &&
            !blockStr.includes("2") &&
            !blockStr.includes("5")
          ) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsHeadgear[0].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Viking
          } else if (
            lastDigit == 9 &&
            blockStr.includes("7") &&
            !blockStr.includes("2") &&
            !blockStr.includes("6") &&
            !blockStr.includes("69")
          ) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsHeadgear[1].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Cowboy
          } else if (
            (lastDigit == 1 ||
              lastDigit == 7 ||
              lastDigit == 3 ||
              lastDigit == 0) &&
            blockStr.includes("8") &&
            !blockStr.includes("6") &&
            !blockStr.includes("2")
          ) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsHeadgear[2].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Halo
          } else if (
            lastDigit == 8 &&
            blockStr.includes("5") &&
            !blockStr.includes("22")
          ) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsHeadgear[3].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Horns
          } else if (lastDigit == 1 && secondLastDigit <= 7) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[0].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Red Bow
          } else if (lastDigit == 2 && secondLastDigit >= 3) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[1].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Bucket Hat
          } else if (lastDigit == 6 && secondLastDigit != 9) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[2].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Baseball Cap
          } else if (lastDigit == 8 && secondLastDigit <= 5) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[3].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Bone Bow
          } else if (lastDigit == 1 && secondLastDigit >= 8) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[4].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Hard Hat
          } else if (lastDigit == 2 && secondLastDigit <= 2) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[5].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Crown
          } else if (lastDigit == 6 && secondLastDigit == 9) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[6].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //MCrown
          } else if (lastDigit == 8 && secondLastDigit >= 6) {
            const hgImg = createImageElement(traits.headgearTraits[7].data);
            root.appendChild(hgImg); //Sun Hat
          }
        }

        // 12. Add clothing if no costume
        if (
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8888") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("0000") &&
          !randomNumberStr.includes("8484")
        ) {
          // Add clothing
          if (
            randomNumberStr.includes("8") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("0") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("1") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("5") &&
            randomNumberStr.includes("2")
          ) {
            const clothingImg = createImageElement(
              traits.randNumTraits[17].data
            );
            root.appendChild(clothingImg); //B0AS Hoodie
          } else if (randomNumberStr.includes("400")) {
            const clothingImg = createImageElement(
              traits.randNumTraits[8].data
            );
            root.appendChild(clothingImg); //Hoodie
          }
          if (
            ((randomNumberStr.includes("8") &&
              randomNumberStr.includes("0") &&
              randomNumberStr.includes("1") &&
              randomNumberStr.includes("5") &&
              randomNumberStr.includes("2")) ||
              randomNumberStr.includes("400")) &&
            parseInt(String(blockStr).slice(-4)) < 3700 &&
            String(blockStr).includes("07")
          ) {
            const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.royalsEyewear[0].data);
            root.appendChild(accsImg); //Laser Eyes
          }
          if (randomNumberStr.includes("79")) {
            const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[2].data);
            root.appendChild(accsImg); //Gold Chain
          }
          if (
            (randomNumberStr.includes("17") && randomNumberStr % 74 == 0) ||
            (randomNumberStr % 17 == 0 && randomNumberStr.includes("74"))
          ) {
            const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[3].data);
            root.appendChild(accsImg); //Pepe Pendant
          }
          if (randomNumberStr.includes("282")) {
            const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[5].data);
            root.appendChild(accsImg); //Crown Pendant
          }
          if (randomNumberStr > 1 && randomNumberStr % 514 == 0) {
            const accsImg = createImageElement(traits.accessories[6].data);
            root.appendChild(accsImg); //Royal Pendant
          }
        }

        // 13. Add costume
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("8888")) {
          const costumeImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[16].data);
          root.appendChild(costumeImg); //Natcat Costume
        }
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("0000")) {
          const costumeImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[4].data);
          root.appendChild(costumeImg); //Space Helmet
        }
        if (randomNumberStr.includes("8484")) {
          const costumeImg = createImageElement(traits.randNumTraits[13].data);
          root.appendChild(costumeImg); //Cyborg Pug
        }

        // Apply extraBackgrounds as the final layer
        if (fifthLastDigit == 7) {
          const overlayImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[2].data);
          root.appendChild(overlayImg); //Periodic Table
        } else if (fifthLastDigit == 6) {
          const overlayImg = createImageElement(traits.extraBackground[5].data);
          root.appendChild(overlayImg); //Jail Bars
        }

        // log details for testing
        if (randomNumberStr != undefined) {
          console.log(randNumStr);
          console.log(randomNumberStr);
          console.log(idNumbersOnly);
          console.log(blockNumber);
        }
      }

      document
        .getElementById("numberInput")
        .addEventListener("input", generateImage);
      document
        .getElementById("inscInput")
        .addEventListener("input", generateImage);

      window.addEventListener("resize", () => {
        const viewer = document.getElementById("viewer");
        const windowWidth = window.innerWidth;
        const windowHeight = window.innerHeight;

        const newSize = Math.min(windowWidth, windowHeight);

        viewer.style.width = `${newSize}px`;
        viewer.style.height = `${newSize}px`;
      });

      window.dispatchEvent(new Event("resize"));
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
